{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21147.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day18.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":300}],"nameAvCenter":"Sayaka","surround":"7009_night_townbuzz","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Owww... Still pretty sore.","textAvColor":"textSayaka","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvCenter":"Sayaka","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]It's healing up, but yeah―@not quite back to normal."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0}],"nameAvCenter":"Sayaka","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Not that I mind the hospital.@Kinda gotten used to the place now."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":200401,"pos":0}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You sure didn't make it easy to find you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Huh?@Uh...do I know you?"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime22","chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","surround":"stop","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You've seen this girl, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":400}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Wait―that's!"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":1}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So you do know her."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I don't know her name or anything, but..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Her name's Mami Tomoe."},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Miss Tomoe..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She's a Magical Girl. Like me.@She and I go back."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But now she's missing.@And I wanna know what's up."},{"chara":[{"id":200601}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I followed her trail as far as the hospital."},{"chara":[{"id":200601}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Snuck in and checked the security footage..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]And the number of people goin' into the Labyrinth@doesn't match the number of people coming back out."},{"chara":[{"id":200601}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mami's on the tape going in...@but there's no sign of her ever leaving."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_063.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Huh?@But she..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So I'm gonna ask you straight."},{"chara":[{"id":200601}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You saw the Labyrinth.@Are you a Magical Girl too?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":201,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]N-no!@I didn't make a contract."},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Unlike Madoka...I didn't have it in me."},{"chara":[{"id":200601}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Madoka?@You mean she..."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"motion":200}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]She made a contract with Kyubey?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
